See docs/GRAPHIFY_MAP.md for full phase graph and file dependency map.

## Git Rules
- Conventional commits: feat / fix / docs / chore / db / refactor / style
- Run lint + typecheck + build before every commit.
- Never commit secrets, .env, or *.db files.
- Never push without explicit user instruction.

